    <note>Zheng(1) Yu(3) [13377] Cai Xiang, WJ, 40.19a-21b; Zheng Xie, WJ, 19.16b-19a; Wang Anshi, WJ, 100.1035-6 (wife #1, born Li(2), who was born in 1000, married him in 1016 at age 17, and died in 1031 at age 32). His wife also came from a wealthy family and married Yu in 1016. The family fortunes of the Zheng had declined and Yu(3) devoted himself solely to scholarship (Xie hints cause and effect, but probable decline owing to Jianzhong's generosity). Xiang drafted the funerary inscription because he was a tongnianyou. CBD, 5, 3659.</note>
